        <apex:pageBlockSection title="Help for sending QuickSMS" columns="1"> 
            
                <p> 1. On the left hand side of the Home Page,on custom link section ,you will find a link called "QuickSms".<br/><br/>
                    2. Click the Link.This will take you to the Quicksms page.<br/><br/>
                    3. Enter all the field.Fields in red are mandatory.<br/><br/>
                    4. Click Send.This will create a Lead into the system and send and SMS to the mobile number
                       which you had provided.
                </p>
            
        </apex:pageBlockSection> 
        </apex:pageBlock>
        
        <apex:pageBlock >
        
        <apex:pageBlockSection title="Help for sending Single Sms from Lead" columns="1">
            
                <p> 1. Go to Lead Tab.Click "New" button.<br/><br/>
                    2. Enter all the information about lead.Don't forget to fill the  mandatory  field,which
                       are marked in "RED" colour.Please  fill the "Mobile" field.Click save.<br/><br/>
                    3. Scroll down you will find a Related list called "SMS Tracker".<br/><br/>
                    4. Click "New SMS".<br/><br/>
                    5. Enter the preferred message which you want to send or  else click on the 
                       Choose Template lookup.Choose the  template which you want to send.The template message
                       will automatically appear on the Text Message Area.<br/><br/>
                    6. Click "Send" button.                
                </p>
        </apex:pageBlockSection>
        </apex:pageBlock>
        
