        <apex:pageBlockSection title="Help for sending Single Sms from Contact" columns="1">
        
                <p> 1. Go to Contact Tab.Click "New" button.<br/><br/>
                    2. Enter all the information about Contact.Don't forget to fill the mandatory field,which
                       are marked in "RED" colour.Please fill the "Mobile" field.Click save.<br/><br/>
