        <apex:pageBlock >
        <apex:pageBlockSection title="Help for sending Bulk Sms from Lead" columns="1">
        
                <p> 1. Go to Lead Tab.Select any "view" and click "Go" button.<br/><br/>
                    2. Select the top most checkbox in order to send message to all the leads in the view.<br/><br/>
                    3. In order to select preferred leads .Select those checkbox.<br/><br/>
                    4. Click "BulkSMSLead button".This will take you to the visual force page,
                       where all the leads select are displayed with there mobile numbers.<br/><br/>
                    5. Enter the preferred message which you want to send or else click on the
                       Choose Template lookup.Choose the template which you want to send.The template message
                       will automatically appear on the Text Message Area.<br/><br/>
                    6. If you want to uncheck some of the Leads,to which you don't want to send sms,you can uncheck the "select" list.As you will
                       uncheck the leads,the lead column will automatically disappear  from the list of selected Leads.<br/><br/>
                    7. If you click the "Reset" button the lead which you had unchecked will automatically appear in the list of all 
                       the selected Leads.<br/><br/>
                    8. Click "Send" button.
                </p>
            
        </apex:pageBlockSection> 
        </apex:pageBlock>
        
