                    5. Enter the preferred message which you want to send or else click on the
                       Choose Template lookup.Choose the template which you want to send.The template message
                       will automatically appear on the Text Message Area.<br/><br/>
                    6. If you want to uncheck some of the Contacts,to which you don't want to send sms,you can uncheck the "select" list.As you will
                       uncheck the leads,the lead column will automatically disappear from the list of selected Contacts.<br/><br/>
                    7. If you click the "Reset" button the contact which you had unchecked will automatically appear in the list of all 
                       the selected Contacts.<br/><br/>
                    8. Click "Send" button.
